h5. Description

In WiKi Markup notation guide, the dash "-" bullet is showed as square, but when applied, it showed disc instead.

h5. Reproduce

Create a new page in confluence and then copy and paste the following WiKi markup, then save.

{noformat}
- ha
- he
- hi
- ho
- hu
{noformat}

h5. Workaround

Go to _Browse > Confluence Admin > Stylesheet_ then paste the following CSS.

{noformat}
ul.alternate {list-style-type:square;}
{noformat}

